OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and largely sunny start.
OL,6,FCloud then builds from the southwest
OL,7,Fthrough the day, with brighter spells
OL,8,Fbecoming more limited through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Many parts staying dry, but
OL,10,Fa few outbreaks of rain possible,
OL,11,Fmainly in the west. Turning breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying cloudy and breezy
OL,14,Fduring the evening, with further
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain. Heavier and more
OL,16,Fpersistent rain spreads northeast
OL,17,Faround midnight, clearing by dawn.
OL,18,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
