OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy with most parts dry,
OL,6,Fbut also a few showers, perhaps heavy.
OL,7,FWarm in any brighter spells that
OL,8,Fdevelop. Heavy rain and gusty winds
OL,9,Fthen move east late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and showers Thursday. Cloudier
OL,13,FFriday, but mostly dry, before a
OL,14,Fweakening band of rain spreads east
OL,15,Flater. Sunny spells and showers
OL,16,FSaturday. Warm in any brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
